verbose_text: Following homology search, strand invasion, alignment, and synapsis, exactly how ALT cancer cells elongate their telomeres is unknown, but a model has been proposed that it proceeds by a specialized homology directed repair (HDR) mechanism that might be similar to break induced replication (BIR).
